WEBVTT

00:00:58.866 --> 00:01:00.333
They're activist investors:

00:01:00.950 --> 00:01:06.867
Carl Icahn, Dan Loeb,
Paul Singer, Barry Rosenstein.

00:01:06.891 --> 00:01:10.474
These are the modern-day
OGs of Wall Street.

00:01:10.498 --> 00:01:11.551
(Laughter)

00:01:11.575 --> 00:01:12.737
These are scary dudes.

00:01:12.761 --> 00:01:14.416
I don't mean Green Goblin scary.

00:01:14.440 --> 00:01:16.655
I mean real scary.

00:01:17.169 --> 00:01:21.814
The fear they strike in the hearts
of a company's CEO and board

00:01:21.838 --> 00:01:23.697
when they enter its stock

00:01:23.721 --> 00:01:28.575
is the same fear you feel
when you hear a bear outside your tent,

00:01:28.599 --> 00:01:29.842
and it's dark,

00:01:29.866 --> 00:01:32.398
and you're sitting there
with a mouthful of Doritos --